  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"100061251\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38f6ab26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5fkMcepNvBqVajc5OupVx6XsfAxgGtCrbapERmBwAOTiazNaGTCmh1A9x5cPP9lYzjxZ9CvcTRV3jA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Astro 凭什么赢得人心？React&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">useCallback</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为何常是“负优化”？本期深入解析岛屿架构与性能迷思，盘点那些听过却不懂的 CSS 冷门函数。职业成长方面，探讨如何拒绝“胶水工作”的伪勤奋、在“表面功夫”文化中突围。此外，还有 Web Components 的杀手锏、AI 时代的前端未来，以及一份 2025 极客节日礼物指南。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <blockquote style=\"display: block;font-size: 0.9em;overflow: auto;overflow-scrolling: touch;border-left: 3px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding-top: 10px;padding-bottom: 10px;border-left-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);margin-top: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 1.2em;padding-right: 1em;padding-left: 1em;border-left-width: 4px;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);quotes: none;\">\n   <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-bottom: 16px;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;margin: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue',\n    'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei',\n    Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(119, 119, 119);line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：Otto 辛宝、TimLi</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">JavaScript Jabber：为什么 Astro 正在赢得开发者青睐（与 Sagi Carmel）- JSJ 697</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 这期节目聊 Astro 为何在一众框架中脱颖而出：内容驱动、服务器优先 + 岛屿架构让站点既快又简单，还能自由集成 React / Vue 等前端栈。Sagi 分享用 Astro 搭建以色列官方人口普查网站的实战，以及如何用作用域 CSS、HTMX 和 View Transitions 减少 JS，又把体验做到顺滑细腻。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.spreaker.com/episode/why-astro-is-winning-developers-over-with-sagi-carmel-jsj-697--68711618\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.spreaker.com/episode/why-astro-is-winning-developers-over-with-sagi-carmel-jsj-697--68711618</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061242\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"196\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2974c66f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5fkMcepNvBqVajc5OupVx6X38KejFkKhKNpKuOqKXxHhtPFlXnceTEpvd6pjTyfzYYsce27fHevAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Developer Tea：职业基础 - 通过专注于主要改进路径避免职业陷阱</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- 许多工程师醉心微小效率提升、刷技能和职场政治，却绕开真正决定上限的「大引擎」。节目用低睾治疗的类比指出：试图靠社交、润简历或「粘合剂工作」来掩盖主线能力不足，只是在给根本问题贴创可贴。主持人拆解「技能收集谬误」，强调放下到处学新栈，把有限工具和业务领域练到极致，通过大量且难度递增的真实问题、刻意走出舒适区来持续成长，成为对核心职责极其可靠的人。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://developertea.com/episodes/9f1af38a-f9af-4df5-9b98-c4dc6a30e366\" target=\"_blank\">https://developertea.com/episodes/9f1af38a-f9af-4df5-9b98-c4dc6a30e366</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061244\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"180\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=af83ee9a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5fkMcepNvBqVajc5OupVx6X8F8mf4zDpgXFexZ2N3TVqRiaBt06ib2gbCBfMXsicWy5bYteBkCrrlSpQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">PodRocket：无用的 useCallback - React 性能误区解析（与 Dominik Dorfmeister）（重播）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Dominik 直言，大多数手写的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">useCallback</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">useMemo</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;并没带来真实性能收益，反而让代码更难读、更难维护。本期拆解手动记忆化在真实项目中为何常常“名存实亡”，介绍 React Compiler 如何自动做对优化，以及何时才真的值得 memo。还会聊到&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;word-wrap: break-word;padding: 2px 4px;border-radius: 4px;margin: 0 2px;background-color: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);font-family: Operator Mono, Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;word-break: break-all;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">latest ref</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;模式、React Compiler ESLint 插件和自评 PR 等实战技巧，帮你重构团队对“性能优化”的思维方式。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgb(199, 201, 204) 0px 0px 0px inset;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;margin-top:12px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;align-items:center;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 0 !important;padding-right: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;flex: 1 1 0%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;justify-content: space-between;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"font-size: 12px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);line-height: 1.75em;font-weight: bold;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\">长按识别二维码查看原文</span></strong>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;margin: 0;font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;text-align: start;white-space: normal;text-size-adjust: auto;font-size: 12px;margin-bottom: 0;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.8;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);word-break: break-all;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"http://podrocket.logrocket.com/the-useless-usecallback-react-performance-myths-dominik-dorfmeister-repeat\" target=\"_blank\">http://podrocket.logrocket.com/the-useless-usecallback-react-performance-myths-dominik-dorfmeister-repeat</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;max-width: 90px;box-sizing: border-box;flex-shrink: 0;font-size: 0px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061245\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"196\" style=\"margin: 0 auto;max-width: 100%;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;border-style: none;display: block;border-radius: 4px;overflow-wrap: break-word;visibility: visible;width: 90px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0034cc6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FINNfEriciaG5fkMcepNvBqVajc5OupVx6XdwsNhB6xCo75ciaOJQXpiauHnLxeUmelpUAE09icvOt6UPf4FdFXia3Mzw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding-top:8px;margin:0;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;padding-bottom:8px;font-size:15px;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Segoe UI', Arial, freesans,\n    sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;word-wrap: break-word;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><span leaf=\"\">Syntax：957 - CSS：高级与冷门</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;- Scott 和 Wes 用一整期 STUMP’d 互相用冷门 CSS 题目挖坑，从形状函数、滚动捕捉、xywh()、ray() 到 cross-fade()、@property、滤镜函数和命名空间，全是“你大概听过却讲不清”的知识点。想给自己的 CSS 脑子做次压力测试、顺便为面试和代码评审多点谈资，这期非常值得边听边记笔记。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:16px 20px;text-size-adjust:auto;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.476px;display:flex;font-size:12px;border-color:rgb(62, 62, 62);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-